author: Jordan Hayne
title: Why health workers are the canary in Canberra's coronavirus coalmine
description: As the COVID-19 outbreak continues to grow, Canberrans are being reassured there's no community transmission in the ACT. But how do we know the virus isn't spreading if we only test people who are already in the risk categories?
content:
